Rules-Requires-Root: no

Package: libminizip-ng3.0
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: same
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: zip manipulation library - runtime
 minizip-ng is a minimalistic library that supports compressing, extracting,
 viewing, and manipulating zip files. It is a fork of the original minizip
 library included with zlib, rewritten and with features added.
 .
 This package includes the shared library.

