Conflicts: libminizip-dev
Replaces: libminizip-dev
Description: zip manipulation library - development
 minizip-ng is a minimalistic library that supports compressing, extracting,
 viewing, and manipulating zip files. It is a fork of the original minizip
 library included with zlib, rewritten and with features added.
 .
 This package includes the development support files.

Package: minizip-ng
Section: utils
Architecture: any
Multi-Arch: foreign
Depends: ${misc:Depends}, ${shlibs:Depends}
Description: zip manipulation library - binaries
 minizip-ng is a minimalistic library that supports compressing, extracting,
 viewing, and manipulating zip files. It is a fork of the original minizip
 library included with zlib, rewritten and with features added.
 .
 This package includes the minizip and minigzip binaries.
